{"tid":81213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大學者花費六年研究：人愈大愈會爆粗","createTime":"2017-01-15T07:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T16:37:38.000Z","uid":58099,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa08d8b409d310b9bb722777bc81b0fc9a12e0a","tid":81213,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hm.people.com.cn/mediafile/200905/06/F200905061658233243910158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhm.people.com.cn%2Fmediafile%2F200905%2F06%2FF200905061658233243910158.jpg&h=21e3185d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】廣東話粗口是校園禁忌，同時卻廣泛流行。理大學者石丹理發表全港首個中學生粗口研究，花6年時間研究，發現青少年講粗口的頻率會隨年齡增加。由讀中一時佔約24%，增加至中六時約43%。研究亦發現，自覺社交、控制情緒商數及分辨是非能力越低的中學生，會傾向講更多粗口。"},{"pid":"8acdad578c48a7af225943b46406734bfc15be1f","tid":81213,"uid":53378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"f6702fbc1da9379319462eabb5ebfa64b4853d38","tid":81213,"uid":5684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 辛苦晒"},{"pid":"de2eb12e306d0ef9e7abe28561b2273964761730","tid":81213,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUZquX9uJYtyXihhT3d5a7qABjkyRk1wmd6Ynr9ARmhA3?filename=o70fN3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo70fN3.gif&h=a2da4952&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dcb5a18025c29cc6db68c9e1135e669db320ca2","tid":81213,"uid":64944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"原~~來阿媽係女人~~~<br />\ndada~~da da da da"},{"pid":"c2ba9692359931ab07a2be5191735cf65117bab1","tid":81213,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"我巴西架碌柒"},{"pid":"a8c65cfe8fcc171338fc2c9613ac2740843b7721","tid":81213,"u